      m_Calls: []
  m_text: '1. Position the striker using the slider.


    2. Charge the striker
    by dragging your finger over it.


    3. Release to shoot it into one of the
    four holes.


    4. Queen''s pocketing gives a +2 bonus.


    Objective:

    Score
    points by pocketing white pieces while preventing the opponent from scoring black
    ones.



    Time limit:

    You have 120 seconds to showcase your skills. Be
    quick!



    Good luck! Enjoy the exciting Carrom Game!'
